<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="健康活動推薦 - 預防肌肉退化、失智症、憂鬱症的運動指南">
    <meta name="keywords" content="健康運動,長輩活動,預防失智,肌肉退化,蝴蝶擁抱法">
    <title>健康活動推薦 - 長輩運動指南</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'PingFang TC', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f8f8f8;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border: 8px solid #000;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .header {
            background: #dc143c;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 8px solid #000;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 30%;
            width: 8px;
            height: 100%;
            background: #000;
        }

        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30%;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
            background: #000;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            z-index: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            z-index: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            min-height: 500px;
        }

        .activity-section {
            padding: 40px;
            border-right: 8px solid #000;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .activity-section:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(1) {
            background: #ffdd00;
            border-bottom: 8px solid #000;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(2) {
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            border-bottom: 8px solid #000;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(3) {
            background: white;
            border-right: 8px solid #000;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(4) {
            background: #ffdd00;
        }

        .activity-title {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .activity-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dc143c;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 4px solid #000;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 10px auto;
            min-width: 200px;
            cursor: pointer;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }

        .activity-link:visited {
            color: white !important;
        }

        .activity-link:hover,
        .activity-link:focus {
            background: #b91c3c;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            outline: none;
        }

        .activity-link:active {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(2) .activity-link {
            background: #ffdd00;
            color: #000 !important;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(2) .activity-link:visited {
            color: #000 !important;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(2) .activity-link:hover,
        .activity-section:nth-child(2) .activity-link:focus {
            background: #ffd700;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(3) .activity-link {
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white !important;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(3) .activity-link:visited {
            color: white !important;
        }

        .activity-section:nth-child(3) .activity-link:hover,
        .activity-section:nth-child(3) .activity-link:focus {
            background: #0052a3;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #000;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            border-top: 8px solid #dc143c;
        }

        .footer .designer {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        /* 響應式設計 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .activity-section {
                border-right: none;
                border-bottom: 8px solid #000;
            }
            
            .activity-section:last-child {
                border-bottom: none;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .activity-title {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
            
            .activity-link {
                font-size: 1.1em;
                padding: 12px 20px;
            }
        }

        /* 增加視覺層次感 */
        .mondrian-accent {
            position: absolute;
            background: #dc143c;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .accent-1 {
            top: 20%;
            right: 0;
            width: 20px;
            height: 40%;
        }

        .accent-2 {
            bottom: 0;
            left: 60%;
            width: 40%;
            height: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <h1>健康活動推薦</h1>
            <p>為您精選的健康運動指南</p>
        </header>
        
        <main class="content">
            <section class="activity-section">
                <div class="mondrian-accent accent-1"></div>
                <h2 class="activity-title">預防肌肉退化</h2>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/shorts/qXZa8WAhoKA" 
                   target="_blank" 
                   rel="noopener noreferrer"
                   class="activity-link"
                   aria-label="觀看預防肌肉退化運動影片">
                   觀看運動影片
                </a>
            </section>
            
            <section class="activity-section">
                <h2 class="activity-title">預防失智症</h2>
                <a href="https://youtu.be/HpTaqv31zcs?si=E80kYpug5Pm0emd9" 
                   target="_blank" 
                   rel="noopener noreferrer"
                   class="activity-link"
                   aria-label="觀看預防失智症運動影片">
                   觀看運動影片
                </a>
            </section>
            
            <section class="activity-section">
                <div class="mondrian-accent accent-2"></div>
                <h2 class="activity-title">預防憂鬱</h2>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lWkCS-g7Y-g" 
                   target="_blank" 
                   rel="noopener noreferrer"
                   class="activity-link"
                   aria-label="觀看蝴蝶擁抱法影片">
                   蝴蝶擁抱法
                </a>
            </section>
            
            <section class="activity-section">
                <h2 class="activity-title">健康生活</h2>
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.2em; color: #666;">
                    持續運動<br>
                    保持身心健康
                </p>
            </section>
        </main>
        
        <footer class="footer">
            <div class="designer">設計師 鍾孟修</div>
            <div>職能治療師</div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
